1
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,480
The "Ji" as in "discipline."

2
00:01:08,439 --> 00:01:09,959
Not the "Ji" as in "season"?

3
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,359
It's this "Ji."

4
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,480
Oh.

5
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:15,840
That Prince Ji you mentioned is still hundreds of miles away.

6
00:01:16,239 --> 00:01:17,040
Huh?

7
00:01:18,239 --> 00:01:19,159
Then I'm not going.

8
00:01:19,159 --> 00:01:20,040
You two go.

9
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,560
Why?

10
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,359
This Prince Ji,

11
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:27,239
since childhood, schemed against me with Liu Heng.

12
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,200
Now, just seeing him

13
00:01:29,319 --> 00:01:30,519
gives me trauma.

14
00:01:31,159 --> 00:01:32,599
You two go in and persuade him.

15
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,359
I'll head into town

16
00:01:34,519 --> 00:01:35,879
for an incognito visit.

17
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,000
Get a feel for the place,

18
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:39,920
and see how the people feel about Prince Ji.

19
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:41,280
Mm.

20
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,640
Go on.

21
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,519
This is Ji City.

22
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,079
Step outside and you'll be conned.

23
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:50,840
I'll show you both

24
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,760
how I survive by sheer wit.

25
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,680
Greetings, Prince Ji.

26
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:04,920
Oh.

27
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:08,759
You must be Special Envoy Qi and Princess Ouyang.

28
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:09,639
Indeed.

29
00:02:09,719 --> 00:02:11,400
Sit, sit, sit.

30
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:12,360
Thank you, Prince Ji.

31
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:18,520
I want to see

32
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:22,120
what kind of man raised such a talent.

33
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:25,120
This time, I absolutely won't be fooled.

34
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:27,680
Bring it out.

35
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,319
Jujube cakes.

36
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,919
Aren't these a specialty of our Yan Kingdom?

37
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:43,159
I haven't had these in ages.

38
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,479
Princess Ouyang,

39
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:48,080
this is a welcome gift, prepared just for you.

40
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,000
Eat, eat.

41
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,680
Over the years,

42
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,159
here in our Ji City,

43
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:03,719
I've implemented a unique style of governance.

44
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,599
I encourage the people

45
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:06,520
to use their heads more,

46
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,039
through wit and strategy.

47
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:09,759
So far,

48
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,680
it's been somewhat effective.

49
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,439
Mm, you're telling me.

50
00:03:13,759 --> 00:03:14,840
We got conned the moment we entered the city.

51
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,680
*coughs*

52
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:19,120
The moment we entered the city,

53
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:19,919
we noticed

54
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:21,919
all the citizens are resourceful and clever,

55
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,520
deeply cultivated.

56
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:25,000
Hahaha!

57
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:26,280
I think so too.

58
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,080
So that's why

59
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,400
I want to spread this policy

60
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,520
across the entire kingdom.

61
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,840
Let everyone in the land

62
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,719
use their brains more,

63
00:03:31,759 --> 00:03:32,800
and brute force less.

64
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,439
Wouldn't you agree?

65
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:35,599
Mm, mm, mm.

66
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,120
Brute force?

67
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:38,919
What?

68
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:42,120
You're looking down on us martial artists?

69
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,520
Can you keep your voice down?

70
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:49,879
Eating his food doesn't soften your tongue, huh?

71
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:54,560
I've heard Princess Ouyang is a martial artist.

72
00:03:54,599 --> 00:03:56,680
So I prepared another gift.

73
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,199
Here.

74
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:06,800
This sword is forged from cold iron from Mount Tai's peak.

75
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,159
Ten craftsmen

76
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:10,719
spent two years forging it.

77
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,360
What do you think?

78
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,879
Haha.

79
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,160
It truly is a fine sword.

80
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:22,240
A fine sword deserves a beauty.

81
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,439
If the Princess likes it,

82
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:26,120
then please accept it

83
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:27,480
as our

84
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:30,120
second gift.

85
00:04:30,519 --> 00:04:31,319
Prince Ji,

86
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,439
you're far too generous.

87
00:04:33,519 --> 00:04:34,319
Hahaha.

88
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,399
Thank you, Prince Ji.

89
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,120
Thank you, Prince Ji.

90
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,040
Hahaha.

91
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:47,480
Such a trifle, and you're already bought.

92
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,360
Hey.

93
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:55,680
Envoy Qi is an imperial scholar.

94
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:58,639
Surely you've studied ancient texts too?

95
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:00,319
Hmm.

96
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,480
Oh my!

97
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,319
Ahem.

98
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:03,480
Oh my goodness!

99
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,160
Oh my, my, my!

100
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:07,360
The Canon of Pure Music!

101
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,439
The legacy of the previous dynasty's Chancellor Wang.

102
00:05:10,759 --> 00:05:12,920
The masterwork of ancient music.

103
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,720
It's the only copy left.

104
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:16,240
How did you manage to find it?

105
00:05:16,839 --> 00:05:18,360
I sought out an old loyalist

106
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,800
and bought it from him at a high price.

107
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,560
You like it?

108
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:26,800
Then it's yours.

109
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:31,079
Oh, I couldn't possibly.

110
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:32,079
Come now.

111
00:05:32,079 --> 00:05:33,199
Take it, take it.

112
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:36,199
And I thought you were so high-minded.

113
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:42,240
Hey.

114
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:43,839
Judging by the Prince's manner,

115
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:44,600
does this mean

116
00:05:44,839 --> 00:05:46,879
you'll return to the capital as Emperor?

117
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:47,800
Of course.

118
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,600
Then would you be willing

119
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,600
to make me your Empress?

120
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:54,560
The Princess has both martial skill and wisdom.

121
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,720
It would be my honor.

122
00:05:57,079 --> 00:05:58,240
Then would you be willing

123
00:05:58,279 --> 00:05:59,439
to not share a bed with me?

124
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:00,160
Oh.

125
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:01,199
On that matter,

126
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:04,079
the Princess's wishes come first, of course.

127
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,439
How thoughtful.

128
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,480
Tell you what,

129
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,720
words alone aren't proof.

130
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:14,000
Let's put it in writing,

131
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:14,639
let's put it in writing,

132
00:06:14,639 --> 00:06:15,879
let's put it in writing,

133
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:17,079
and settle it now.

134
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:18,079
Fine.

135
00:06:18,199 --> 00:06:19,000
Go on.

136
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,759
The Princess is indeed decisive.

137
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,920
Good.

138
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,040
It's settled then.

139
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,000
This is

140
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,240
way too fast.

141
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,600
This Prince Ji

142
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:55,839
is exactly the man we've been looking for.

143
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:58,439
I didn't expect the ending

144
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,680
to come so suddenly.

145
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:06,079
That chicken farmer dared to talk about me like that.

146
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,439
I'll prove him wrong.

147
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:08,920
We won't be fooled,

148
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,639
right?

149
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,800
Oh, I'm so hungry.

150
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,519
Candied Hawthorn Skewers!

151
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,360
Hey, my good man.

152
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:16,839
How much for these Candied Hawthorn Skewers?

153
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:17,120
Ah, ah, ah!

154
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:17,680
Ah, ah, ah!

155
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,000
Five copper coins.

156
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:18,720
That cheap?

157
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,920
That cheap?

158
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,839
We'll start with ten skewers.

159
00:07:21,519 --> 00:07:22,319
Cheap?

160
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:25,439
I've sold these skewers for years,

161
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:27,240
and nobody's ever called them cheap.

162
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:42,800
Oh no

163
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:45,160
Got so caught up talking, forgot to give Prince Ji the jade

164
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:46,399
Hey, my friend

165
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:47,439
Don't get the wrong idea

166
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,720
We just got here

167
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,120
We don't know the prices around here yet

168
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:50,759
Oh?

169
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:51,240
Out with it

170
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:55,839
Are you spies from another hawthorn stall?

171
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:59,360
Trying to steal our secret family recipe?

172
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,120
Huh?

173
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:00,680
Hey

174
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,879
Why do people around here

175
00:08:01,879 --> 00:08:03,279
always assume the worst of others?

176
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:03,439
Hmph

177
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,519
Aren't you about to say

178
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:06,720
that our Candied Hawthorn Skewers

179
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,399
are cheap?

180
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,199
And lower my guard

181
00:08:09,199 --> 00:08:10,079
to get me to reveal

182
00:08:10,079 --> 00:08:11,319
our secret family recipe

183
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,279
which is 30% brown sugar

184
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:14,399
65% white sugar, and 5% osmanthus sugar

185
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:17,360
boiled into syrup?

186
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,319
We really don't care, okay?

187
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,399
Oh-ho-ho-ho!

188
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,920
You stole our secret family recipe!

189
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,319
Now then

190
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,920
Hand over ten taels of silver

191
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,720
Otherwise

192
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,759
I'll drag you before the magistrate

193
00:08:31,199 --> 00:08:32,000
Hey

194
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,440
I wasn't eavesdropping

195
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:35,080
You just told me yourself, remember?

196
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:38,600
Somebody!

197
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,559
Help, somebody!

198
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:41,480
Someone stole our secret family recipe!

199
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,480
Help, somebody!

200
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:43,440
Here, take it, take it

201
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,200
Zhenzhen, let's go, quick

202
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:55,960
Prince Ji

203
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,480
Yes?

204
00:08:56,679 --> 00:08:57,720
Special Envoy Qi has arrived

205
00:08:57,879 --> 00:08:58,679
Come, look at this

206
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,639
This is a map of our Great Liang Kingdom

207
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:03,919
Vast in territory

208
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,399
but poorly administered

209
00:09:06,039 --> 00:09:06,840
Sigh

210
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:08,600
Right now, currency

211
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:09,639
language

212
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:10,879
and units of measure

213
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:12,000
have yet to be unified

214
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,559
But that's no matter

215
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:14,720
All of these

216
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,840
are the great works I'll accomplish someday

217
00:09:18,799 --> 00:09:20,360
Such foresight from Prince Ji is rare

218
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,360
I'm truly impressed

219
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:22,480
Special Envoy Qi

220
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:23,799
I

221
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:25,200
know you're a man of great learning

222
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,320
And your current treatment at the palace

223
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,480
truly wastes your talent

224
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,399
But don't worry

225
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:33,200
Once I become Emperor

226
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:36,200
I'll give you a post where you can truly shine

227
00:09:36,279 --> 00:09:37,080
Ha

228
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:38,919
Many thanks for Prince Ji's kind regard

229
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:39,360
However

230
00:09:45,159 --> 00:09:45,799
Your Highness

231
00:09:45,799 --> 00:09:47,639
The refreshments you ordered for the princess

232
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:48,360
are ready now

233
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:48,679
Oh

234
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:49,519
Just leave them over there

235
00:09:49,519 --> 00:09:50,320
I'll grab them myself later

236
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:50,799
Yes, Your Highness.

237
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:51,320
What did you say?

238
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:52,960
Huh?

239
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:53,759
I...

240
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,840
Aren't you going to see the princess soon?

241
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:56,679
Hmm

242
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,080
To tell you the truth

243
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:03,799
My mother won't approve my marriage to Ouyang Yan

244
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,720
She says she's too wild

245
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:06,480
Not at all

246
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,279
Ouyang Yan

247
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:09,080
is kind-hearted and gentle

248
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:09,960
and warm

249
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:11,519
She can even protect me when it matters

250
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:12,720
Pro... protect you?

251
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:13,759
That's right

252
00:10:13,759 --> 00:10:14,759
That's what I think too

253
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:16,399
But the ministers won't agree

254
00:10:16,639 --> 00:10:17,000
Hmm

255
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:20,080
I'm not saying there's anything wrong with her

256
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,720
It's just that as Empress

257
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:24,600
isn't she a bit unpresentable?

258
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:27,440
Special Envoy Qi

259
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,759
Honestly speaking

260
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:31,320
is she really fit to guide the people

261
00:10:31,559 --> 00:10:32,639
as the mother of the nation, the Empress?

262
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:34,200
Well

263
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,879
What matters is what you think

264
00:10:38,159 --> 00:10:38,720
I...

265
00:10:39,879 --> 00:10:41,080
I want to break off the engagement

266
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,159
Then how are you going to tell her?

267
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:44,960
Just tell her the truth

268
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,679
No way

269
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:49,279
If she can't become Empress and restore the kingdom because of her own faults,

270
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:50,600
she'd cry her heart out

271
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,799
Then what do we do?

272
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:57,320
Ah

273
00:10:57,799 --> 00:10:59,039
I'll go tell her for you

274
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:01,240
But you have to promise me

275
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,759
Even if she can't become Empress

276
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:03,840
you must still help her restore the kingdom

277
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:04,879
No problem

278
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:06,879
Then this matter

279
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:08,080
I'll leave it to you

280
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:10,799
Fine

281
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:13,279
Wait, no, I still can't trust you

282
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,120
Here, let's do this

283
00:11:16,519 --> 00:11:17,559
Look at this

284
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:19,159
The late Emperor left it for the Crown Prince

285
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,639
The Crown Prince gave it to me when I left the palace

286
00:11:22,159 --> 00:11:25,200
He said once I found a prince fit to be Emperor

287
00:11:25,279 --> 00:11:27,320
I should give him this as a token

288
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,120
Hey, that's me!

289
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,360
If you dare go back on your word

290
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,759
I'll smash it to pieces

291
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,840
A gentleman's word is his bond

292
00:11:36,399 --> 00:11:37,360
Let me have a look first

293
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,000
Hey

294
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:38,720
No way

295
00:11:39,679 --> 00:11:40,840
I'll hold onto it for you

296
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,039
Oh

297
00:11:42,039 --> 00:11:43,360
Send those refreshments to my room

298
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,240
I'm going to find her

299
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:45,759
Ah, yes, yes, yes

300
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:46,639
Send them

301
00:11:47,759 --> 00:11:47,960
Send them

302
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,440
Send them over

303
00:11:57,559 --> 00:11:57,759
Send them

304
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,279
Send them over

305
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:03,360
Someone come here

306
00:12:03,639 --> 00:12:04,639
Send them over

307
00:12:20,519 --> 00:12:22,960
Don't come near me when I'm training.

308
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,039
It's dangerous.

309
00:12:25,279 --> 00:12:27,080
After we're married, I'll teach you a few moves.

310
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,039
For self-defense.

311
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:31,120
You've trained in martial arts since childhood?

312
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:37,200
My father didn't want me to train at first.

313
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:38,360
It's just that...

314
00:12:38,519 --> 00:12:39,879
I was just too gifted.

315
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:41,480
I mastered it on my own.

316
00:12:42,919 --> 00:12:44,039
Then to restore the kingdom of Yan

317
00:12:44,039 --> 00:12:45,279
all depends on you, Princess.

318
00:12:45,919 --> 00:12:46,720
Heh.

319
00:12:46,919 --> 00:12:49,559
If I could restore the kingdom alone,

320
00:12:49,759 --> 00:12:51,399
I wouldn't have to become Empress.

321
00:12:51,559 --> 00:12:52,200
Hahaha.

322
00:12:53,279 --> 00:12:54,600
You're quite honest, Princess.

323
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:58,120
Since we've signed the engagement agreement,

324
00:12:58,120 --> 00:13:01,000
I don't have to act like a lady anymore.

325
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,559
I know you're no lady.

326
00:13:05,679 --> 00:13:07,559
Special Envoy Qi already told me.

327
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,440
He badmouthed me to you?

328
00:13:12,039 --> 00:13:13,399
What else did he say about me?

329
00:13:15,759 --> 00:13:16,559
Hmph.

330
00:13:17,559 --> 00:13:20,120
Just wait till I give him a good lesson.

331
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:21,159
No need.

332
00:13:21,559 --> 00:13:23,120
Your mission is complete.

333
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,159
I don't think

334
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,759
you two will ever meet again.

335
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,240
Why?

336
00:13:28,519 --> 00:13:29,840
You're going to be Empress.

337
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,879
An Empress belongs in the inner palace.

338
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,320
He's a court minister.

339
00:13:33,559 --> 00:13:35,399
What reason would you have to meet again?

340
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:42,200
I hadn't thought about that.

341
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:48,440
But Qi Zhi is quite talented.

342
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,399
I was thinking

343
00:13:49,399 --> 00:13:51,759
he could help me restore the kingdom later.

344
00:13:51,879 --> 00:13:53,360
Hahaha.

345
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,960
He's just a chicken farmer.

346
00:13:56,919 --> 00:13:58,240
The Liang Kingdom is full of talent.

347
00:13:58,240 --> 00:14:00,559
I'll find you much better help then.

348
00:14:00,879 --> 00:14:01,879
Besides,

349
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:03,799
to secure the prince's succession,

350
00:14:03,799 --> 00:14:05,440
you spent months together day and night.

351
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:07,039
Feelings are bound to develop.

352
00:14:07,519 --> 00:14:09,200
As the future Emperor,

353
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:11,159
how could I let you meet again?

354
00:14:11,759 --> 00:14:12,399
Who?

355
00:14:12,399 --> 00:14:13,799
Who has feelings for him?

356
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:15,919
I...

357
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,320
Me and him...

358
00:14:20,159 --> 00:14:21,759
He and I are just partners.

359
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:24,679
A fool like him?

360
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:28,440
I could take down three of him with one strike.

361
00:14:29,039 --> 00:14:31,679
You really have no feelings for him?

362
00:14:34,159 --> 00:14:35,000
Of course not!

363
00:14:35,039 --> 00:14:35,840
Good.

364
00:14:35,879 --> 00:14:36,799
Then get rid of him for me.

365
00:14:38,919 --> 00:14:39,799
What do you mean?

366
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:41,840
Qi Zhi has traveled all over Liang.

367
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:44,519
He's close with princes in every city.

368
00:14:44,799 --> 00:14:47,120
Can I keep such a man by my side?

369
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:49,200
My rule is: never use those you doubt.

370
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:50,639
Especially not Qi Zhi.

371
00:14:50,639 --> 00:14:52,080
Not only can he not be used,

372
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,639
he must be eliminated.

373
00:15:00,879 --> 00:15:01,679
Hey

374
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,559
What brings you here?

375
00:15:03,759 --> 00:15:05,080
I was just about to look for you.

376
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,080
Uh

377
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:07,879
These are your favorite tea snacks.

378
00:15:08,919 --> 00:15:09,399
Looking for me?

379
00:15:09,679 --> 00:15:09,879
Oh

380
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:12,519
Is something up?

381
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,159
Nothing in particular.

382
00:15:14,159 --> 00:15:15,360
Just wanted to chat.

383
00:15:15,519 --> 00:15:15,840
Sure.

384
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:19,360
Princess

385
00:15:20,039 --> 00:15:21,879
Have you forgotten your mission?

386
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:24,600
The people of Yan are all counting on you.

387
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:25,720
You're threatening me?

388
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,600
I can't believe you'd think of me this way.

389
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:29,240
You've really disappointed me.

390
00:15:29,639 --> 00:15:30,440
That's right.

391
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,399
I am threatening you.

392
00:15:33,039 --> 00:15:33,840
The Empress's throne

393
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:35,240
or Qi Zhi

394
00:15:35,639 --> 00:15:37,279
You can only choose one.

395
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,120
Despicable!

396
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,240
A man like that

397
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:45,279
isn't worth marrying anyway.

398
00:15:46,559 --> 00:15:47,759
What a pity.

399
00:15:48,799 --> 00:15:50,480
The princess is loyal and devoted,

400
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:51,679
but her affection

401
00:15:51,879 --> 00:15:53,080
has been given to the wrong man.

402
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,200
What do you mean?

403
00:15:56,919 --> 00:15:57,799
Heh, what do I mean?

404
00:15:58,799 --> 00:16:01,559
If you hadn't brought that chicken out of the palace,

405
00:16:02,399 --> 00:16:04,519
would Hua Hua have ended up as soup?

406
00:16:05,519 --> 00:16:06,720
How do you know about Hua Hua?

407
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:07,600
Heh heh heh.

408
00:16:07,639 --> 00:16:09,039
How do I know?

409
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:12,080
Special Envoy Qi has been bitter about it.

410
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:13,480
To be honest,

411
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:14,799
he came to see me just now.

412
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,440
And he said that you, Princess,

413
00:16:16,919 --> 00:16:18,039
are far too savage,

414
00:16:18,639 --> 00:16:20,240
unable to enlighten the people,

415
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:22,519
and unworthy of being Empress.

416
00:16:22,759 --> 00:16:24,240
He even asked me to break off the marriage.

417
00:16:25,039 --> 00:16:26,600
He said he could handle you,

418
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,919
in exchange for a promotion in rank.

419
00:16:27,919 --> 00:16:28,639
Shut up!

420
00:16:29,039 --> 00:16:30,240
He's not that kind of person.

421
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:33,519
He even prepared your favorite snacks,

422
00:16:33,519 --> 00:16:35,080
just to win you over.

423
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:35,919
Impossible.

424
00:16:36,519 --> 00:16:37,720
If you don't believe me,

425
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:38,840
go see for yourself.

426
00:16:47,519 --> 00:16:48,879
Ah, mm.

427
00:16:49,159 --> 00:16:52,840
What do you think of Prince Ji?

428
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:54,679
He's pretty great.

429
00:16:55,159 --> 00:16:56,320
Handsome and distinguished.

430
00:16:56,519 --> 00:16:57,559
Skilled at governing.

431
00:16:58,639 --> 00:16:59,519
No, that's not it.

432
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:00,519
Just think about it.

433
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,320
The moment you entered the city,

434
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:04,960
you got tricked by the people of Ji City.

435
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:07,559
A prince who raises citizens like that,

436
00:17:07,559 --> 00:17:08,119
do you actually like him?

437
00:17:08,519 --> 00:17:08,720
Huh?

438
00:17:09,519 --> 00:17:10,559
Think about it some more.

439
00:17:10,559 --> 00:17:11,839
Once he becomes emperor,

440
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:13,160
will he even marry you?

441
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:13,680
Huh?

442
00:17:14,519 --> 00:17:15,720
And after he marries you,

443
00:17:15,799 --> 00:17:17,279
will he treat you well?

444
00:17:17,359 --> 00:17:17,559
Huh?

445
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:20,880
Huh?

446
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:25,319
Every prince has his own way of ruling.

447
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:26,680
You wouldn't understand.

448
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:29,039
You can't just say he's no good.

449
00:17:29,279 --> 00:17:32,799
Hey, you're using my own words against me?

450
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,480
You've got some nerve.

451
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:38,319
Your words don't add up.

452
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:40,039
You keep dodging the question.

453
00:17:40,279 --> 00:17:41,079
Spit it out.

454
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:43,880
What are you really trying to tell me?

455
00:17:44,799 --> 00:17:47,039
Are you trying to talk me out of marrying Prince Ji?

456
00:17:47,599 --> 00:17:48,960
You want me to call off the engagement?

457
00:17:50,079 --> 00:17:51,359
How did you know?

458
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:54,000
You sneak.

459
00:17:55,319 --> 00:17:56,240
Zhenzhen.

460
00:17:56,359 --> 00:17:57,680
I'm so tired from walking.

461
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:58,960
Why don't we just head back?

462
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:00,920
I'm starving.

463
00:18:01,119 --> 00:18:01,920
Huh?

464
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:03,039
Hold on a sec.

465
00:18:05,119 --> 00:18:05,920
Here you go.

466
00:18:10,359 --> 00:18:11,480
You want one too?

467
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:13,279
No.

468
00:18:13,279 --> 00:18:14,480
I don't like sweet things.

469
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:15,720
And I don't eat sour things either.

470
00:18:17,480 --> 00:18:18,279
Oh right, Zhenzhen.

471
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:20,359
Do you like reading shojo manga?

472
00:18:21,039 --> 00:18:21,920
Nope.

473
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:23,400
A boy and girl in love is so boring.

474
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:26,799
Okay then.

475
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:32,519
But if you drew it, I'd read it.

476
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:34,039
Really?

477
00:18:35,119 --> 00:18:35,920
That's wonderful.

478
00:18:38,079 --> 00:18:38,880
Hey.

479
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,680
I'm still so hungry.

480
00:18:43,599 --> 00:18:45,599
But I'm out of money too.

481
00:18:47,559 --> 00:18:49,039
I just thought of a great idea.

482
00:18:49,799 --> 00:18:50,599
Come take a look, come see!

483
00:18:50,599 --> 00:18:51,440
Take a look, have a peek!

484
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:52,799
Professional portraits!

485
00:18:52,839 --> 00:18:53,519
Come take a look!

486
00:18:53,519 --> 00:18:53,920
Come on, have a look!

487
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:54,680
Come take a look!

488
00:18:54,839 --> 00:18:55,839
Professional portraits!

489
00:18:58,640 --> 00:18:59,440
Sir.

490
00:18:59,839 --> 00:19:00,839
Would you like a portrait?

491
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:05,759
Please, have a seat, sir.

492
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:09,960
Listen, I'll tell you something.

493
00:19:10,039 --> 00:19:11,400
Make me look really handsome.

494
00:19:11,799 --> 00:19:12,799
My family back home

495
00:19:12,799 --> 00:19:15,000
is using this portrait to find me a wife.

496
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:17,200
Don't you worry, sir.

497
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:18,680
I've been painting for 18 years.

498
00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:19,799
I'll definitely paint you

499
00:19:19,799 --> 00:19:20,759
looking just like Adonis.

500
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:35,680
Sir, take a look

501
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:40,680
So ugly, so ugly!

502
00:19:41,599 --> 00:19:42,599
How could it be ugly?

503
00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:44,200
It looks exactly like you!

504
00:19:45,359 --> 00:19:46,880
You wicked painter!

505
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:49,400
This painting gave me a heart attack!

506
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:52,000
Pay me ten taels of silver

507
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,720
Or I'll drag you to the authorities

508
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:56,119
Ten taels of silver?

509
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:58,680
I already paid ten taels to the last guy

510
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:00,880
Sir, if you really had a heart attack

511
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:02,440
Then I'll have to take you to a doctor

512
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,279
Fine

513
00:20:06,319 --> 00:20:07,599
A doctor it is, then

514
00:20:08,480 --> 00:20:09,279
Despicable!

515
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:11,039
Two-faced hypocrite!

516
00:20:11,519 --> 00:20:13,640
Screaming threats daily, how can you be Empress?

517
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:14,279
I...

518
00:20:17,799 --> 00:20:18,000
Hey!

519
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:19,039
Bookworm

520
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:22,519
That was a really dirty move, you know.

521
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:25,240
Which dirt tunnel did you crawl out of?

522
00:20:26,799 --> 00:20:27,599
Bookworm

523
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:30,039
Even if you think Ouyang Yan

524
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:32,839
Is savage, crude, and uncultured

525
00:20:33,279 --> 00:20:35,799
You can't ruin her lifelong happiness

526
00:20:36,079 --> 00:20:37,640
She ruined it herself, okay?

527
00:20:40,119 --> 00:20:40,319
Ha!

528
00:20:41,359 --> 00:20:43,359
So this is how you really feel

529
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:47,480
And you said you prepared fine food and wine for me

530
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:50,000
Guilty conscience, huh?

531
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:50,519
Hey, hey, hey

532
00:20:54,119 --> 00:20:54,319
Hey!

533
00:20:55,359 --> 00:20:56,839
It's poisoned! Poisoned!

534
00:20:58,119 --> 00:20:58,640
Poisoned!

535
00:20:58,640 --> 00:20:59,319
So!

536
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,200
You actually...

537
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:03,599
You actually dared to poison me!

538
00:21:03,759 --> 00:21:04,680
Hey, hey, hey!

539
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:05,880
Calm down, would you?

540
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:07,160
Let me tell you the truth

541
00:21:07,160 --> 00:21:08,480
It's because Prince Ji said

542
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:12,160
His mother and ministers oppose you as his Empress

543
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:14,039
So I came to kindly warn you

544
00:21:14,519 --> 00:21:15,319
All these things

545
00:21:15,359 --> 00:21:16,599
Were all prepared

546
00:21:20,079 --> 00:21:21,920
By Prince Ji

547
00:21:31,200 --> 00:21:32,279
Doctor!

548
00:21:32,279 --> 00:21:33,519
This man's having a heart attack!

549
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:36,039
Oh my, oh my

550
00:21:36,039 --> 00:21:36,559
Quick, quick, quick

551
00:21:36,559 --> 00:21:37,359
Sit over here

552
00:21:41,279 --> 00:21:41,480
Your hand

553
00:21:49,319 --> 00:21:50,720
How did he get sick?

554
00:21:53,359 --> 00:21:53,599
Oh dear

555
00:21:53,599 --> 00:21:55,000
He got scared by my painting

556
00:21:55,720 --> 00:21:57,359
This illness is hard to cure

557
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:58,720
We'll have to use my family's

558
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:01,839
Ancestral thousand-year ginseng

559
00:22:02,359 --> 00:22:03,680
Only then will it work

560
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:04,799
Doctor

561
00:22:05,279 --> 00:22:06,799
I know what you're up to

562
00:22:07,119 --> 00:22:09,160
But we really don't have a single coin

563
00:22:09,359 --> 00:22:10,440
Please have some mercy

564
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:11,279
Don't try to fool me

565
00:22:11,279 --> 00:22:12,759
Saving him is what matters!

566
00:22:13,359 --> 00:22:14,640
No money, no treatment

567
00:22:15,559 --> 00:22:16,359
Out, out, out

568
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:17,759
Hurry up and leave

569
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:18,960
Get out!

570
00:22:19,559 --> 00:22:20,799
Then what about him?

571
00:22:21,279 --> 00:22:21,480
Him?

572
00:22:21,759 --> 00:22:22,559
Right!

573
00:22:22,799 --> 00:22:23,559
He's not sick

574
00:22:23,559 --> 00:22:24,119
Not sick

575
00:22:24,119 --> 00:22:24,640
Impossible

576
00:22:24,640 --> 00:22:25,480
Look at him

577
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:27,200
Oh my, oh my

578
00:22:33,279 --> 00:22:34,519
Do you even know how to do business?

579
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:37,640
Him, him, him!

580
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:38,599
You see that?

581
00:22:40,559 --> 00:22:41,440
Young man

582
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:43,640
I suggest you leave Ji City right away

583
00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:44,200
Huh?

584
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:45,960
If you stay any longer

585
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:47,279
you'll lose your life

586
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:48,440
Farewell

587
00:22:48,519 --> 00:22:49,319
Wait

588
00:22:52,319 --> 00:22:54,759
You haven't paid me for the pulse reading

589
00:22:56,279 --> 00:22:56,759
I...

590
00:22:57,440 --> 00:22:58,920
I thought you were a good person

591
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:00,039
A good person?

592
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:01,240
Don't forget

593
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,519
This is Ji City

594
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:04,000
Oh my

595
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:04,680
Prince Ji

596
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:07,519
Your Sowing Discord scheme really isn't very clever

597
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:09,279
My plan was flawless

598
00:23:09,519 --> 00:23:10,559
How did you find out?

599
00:23:11,480 --> 00:23:14,440
You raised a populace fond of scheming

600
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,279
And in the end

601
00:23:15,279 --> 00:23:16,960
you fell right into their hands

602
00:23:17,079 --> 00:23:17,960
Didn't see that coming, did you?

603
00:23:19,039 --> 00:23:20,440
What does that prove?

604
00:23:20,480 --> 00:23:21,920
That proves nothing

605
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:24,640
But we intercepted your carrier pigeon to Prince Twenty-Eight

606
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:27,079
We've read all your messages

607
00:23:28,359 --> 00:23:29,960
You despicable villain, I...

608
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:33,880
You'd actually side with him?

609
00:23:35,039 --> 00:23:36,440
Me, side with him?

610
00:23:37,319 --> 00:23:38,119
Liu Heng

611
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:39,839
You insult me!

612
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,880
Since I'm destined to be Emperor

613
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:43,160
that means both you and him

614
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,519
I can't let a single one live

615
00:23:44,559 --> 00:23:45,359
First, I'll get rid of you

616
00:23:45,359 --> 00:23:46,480
then I'll get rid of Liu Heng

617
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:48,920
With that scrawny frame of yours

618
00:23:49,039 --> 00:23:50,079
one slash from me

619
00:23:50,319 --> 00:23:51,519
Oh-ho-ho-ho!

620
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:53,039
What's wrong?

621
00:23:53,039 --> 00:23:53,799
Legs going weak, huh?

622
00:23:53,799 --> 00:23:55,000
Hey, hey, hey

623
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:56,759
So, how is it?

624
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:58,160
My tea tastes good, right?

625
00:23:58,480 --> 00:24:00,200
We didn't drink your tea at all

626
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:03,039
Let me tell you

627
00:24:03,039 --> 00:24:04,880
This is a poison I developed myself

628
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:06,640
It's called Must-Hit Powder

629
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:07,960
You don't even have to drink it

630
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:09,599
Just one whiff in the air

631
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:11,480
and you're poisoned

632
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:14,279
Even if you kill us, the court won't spare you

633
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:17,240
A poison that only kills people

634
00:24:17,640 --> 00:24:19,319
would be far too inelegant

635
00:24:20,799 --> 00:24:21,960
This poison

636
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:23,319
every once in a while

637
00:24:23,599 --> 00:24:26,079
makes you uncontrollably want to hit people

638
00:24:27,319 --> 00:24:28,400
The longer it goes

639
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:29,440
the deeper the toxin sinks in

640
00:24:29,519 --> 00:24:30,359
In the end

641
00:24:30,359 --> 00:24:31,920
either you beat someone to death

642
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:33,680
or you exhaust yourself to death

643
00:24:35,400 --> 00:24:36,440
Guards!

644
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:38,960
Lock them up for me

645
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:42,880
Let's see who beats whom to death in the end

646
00:24:43,759 --> 00:24:44,720
Come, royal brother

647
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:44,920
Cheers

648
00:24:45,279 --> 00:24:45,480
Cheers

649
00:24:51,480 --> 00:24:52,279
Brother.

650
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:53,640
Come to think of it,

651
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:55,000
I really should thank you this time.

652
00:24:55,480 --> 00:24:56,640
You have no idea

653
00:24:56,920 --> 00:24:59,160
how those two tormented me the whole way.

654
00:24:59,839 --> 00:25:00,880
But it worked out well,

655
00:25:01,039 --> 00:25:03,200
you helped me get rid of two thorns in my side at once.

656
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,160
Don't mention it.

657
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,000
Brother,

658
00:25:07,440 --> 00:25:09,359
after all this time apart,

659
00:25:09,839 --> 00:25:12,720
your scheming has truly reached godlike levels.

660
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:13,960
No, no, can't compare.

661
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:14,480
I'm impressed.

662
00:25:14,480 --> 00:25:15,279
You flatter me.

663
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:16,920
I was just thinking,

664
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:17,920
back when we were kids,

665
00:25:18,319 --> 00:25:20,000
the way we'd bully the Crown Prince together,

666
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:20,839
it's still vivid in my mind.

667
00:25:20,839 --> 00:25:22,000
You bet it is.

668
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:23,240
Brother,

669
00:25:23,240 --> 00:25:24,000
how about this:

670
00:25:24,319 --> 00:25:26,160
once I, Liu Heng, become emperor,

671
00:25:26,519 --> 00:25:27,359
I'll definitely

672
00:25:27,480 --> 00:25:29,119
write your story into the history books

673
00:25:29,119 --> 00:25:30,480
so everyone in the realm will sing your praises.

674
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:31,160
How does that sound?

675
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:31,799
Oh?

676
00:25:32,079 --> 00:25:33,160
And how would you write it?

677
00:25:34,759 --> 00:25:35,920
With our friendship,

678
00:25:35,920 --> 00:25:38,000
of course I'd write it however you want.

679
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,160
Then write it like this:

680
00:25:41,960 --> 00:25:42,759
Prince Ji,

681
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:45,400
the thirteenth emperor of Da Liang,

682
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:46,480
diligent in rule and beloved by his people.

683
00:25:46,480 --> 00:25:46,920
Haha.

684
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:47,559
Sure.

685
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:50,200
Brother,

686
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:52,039
quit messing around.

687
00:25:56,920 --> 00:25:59,319
Are you really that dumb, or just pretending?

688
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,640
You think I helped you

689
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:03,359
because I wanted you to be emperor?

690
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:05,079
And you call yourself my best friend?

691
00:26:05,079 --> 00:26:06,400
You don't know me at all.

692
00:26:06,759 --> 00:26:07,559
Let me tell you,

693
00:26:07,559 --> 00:26:09,279
that cup of wine you just drank,

694
00:26:09,279 --> 00:26:12,079
I already laced it with Ji City's most widespread,

695
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:13,880
most beloved poison among our people:

696
00:26:14,319 --> 00:26:15,599
Must-Hit Powder.

697
00:26:15,599 --> 00:26:16,440
Before long,

698
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:18,319
you'll just keep hitting and hitting and hitting,

699
00:26:18,359 --> 00:26:19,720
until you exhaust yourself to death.

700
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:21,079
Ouch!

701
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:26,440
Can you go easy on me?

702
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:29,039
This drug stirs up rage.

703
00:26:29,119 --> 00:26:30,400
I don't want to either.

704
00:26:30,759 --> 00:26:32,559
What are you so angry at me for?

705
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:35,480
What's your relationship with Yun Xi?

706
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:36,759
Didn't I already tell you?

707
00:26:37,039 --> 00:26:38,000
Childhood friends.

708
00:26:38,359 --> 00:26:39,759
Why don't I believe that?

709
00:26:39,799 --> 00:26:41,599
Every time I ask, you hem and haw.

710
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:42,440
Qi Zhi!

711
00:26:43,079 --> 00:26:43,880
Ouyang Yan!

712
00:26:44,559 --> 00:26:45,359
Where are you?

713
00:26:49,039 --> 00:26:49,839
Chicken farmer!

714
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:54,200
Women love jumping to conclusions.

715
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:56,839
So what if I jump to conclusions?

716
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:59,640
What are we to each other that you get to guess?

717
00:27:00,240 --> 00:27:01,039
I...

718
00:27:02,799 --> 00:27:04,279
I'm someone who wants to hit you.

719
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:06,880
You're clearly using the poison as an excuse to hit me!

720
00:27:09,559 --> 00:27:10,359
That's right.

721
00:27:10,759 --> 00:27:12,400
Poison or not, I'd still hit you.
